'''1-溴-4-碘苯'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>BrI。

==制备==
1-溴-4-碘苯可由4-溴苯基三氟硼酸钾和[[三碘化铯|三碘化铯]]在[[N,N-二甲基甲酰胺|DMF]]的水溶液中加热反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Tetrahedron|volume=68|issue=19|language=en|date=2012-05|pages=3738–3743|doi=10.1016/j.tet.2012.03.016|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040402012003341|title=Halodeboronation of organotrifluoroborates using tetrabutylammonium tribromide or cesium triiodide|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=Min-Liang Yao, George W. Kabalka, David W. Blevins, Marepally Srinivasa Reddy, Li Yong|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629224745/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040402012003341|dead-url=no}}</ref>4-溴苯重氮盐<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Letters in Organic Chemistry|volume=15|issue=7|language=en|date=2018-06-13|pages=594–599|doi=10.2174/1570178614666170907120329|url=http://www.eurekaselect.com/155407/article|title=An Efficient Gram Scale Synthesis of Aryl Iodides from Aryl Diazofluoroborates in Water under Mild Conditions|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=Somnath S. Gholap|archive-date=2020-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200123022948/http://www.eurekaselect.com/155407/article|dead-url=no}}</ref>或1-溴-4-(三甲基硅基)苯<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|volume=57|issue=2|language=en|date=2018-01-08|pages=442–445|doi=10.1002/anie.201711293|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/anie.201711293|title=Electrochemical Synthesis of Aryl Iodides by Anodic Iododesilylation|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=Robert Möckel, Jessica Hille, Erik Winterling, Stephan Weidemüller, Tabea Melanie Faber, Gerhard Hilt}}</ref>和[[碘化钾|碘化钾]]的反应也可制得1-溴-4-碘苯。

其它制法还包括4-溴苯肼盐酸盐和[[碘|碘]]的反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=ACS Omega|volume=3|issue=8|language=en|issn=2470-1343|date=2018-08-31|pages=9814–9821|doi=10.1021/acsomega.8b01559|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acsomega.8b01559|title=Synthesis of Aryl Iodides from Arylhydrazines and Iodine|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=Chun-ping Dong, Kentaro Nakamura, Toshihide Taniguchi, Soichiro Mita, Shintaro Kodama, Shin-ichi Kawaguchi, Akihiro Nomoto, Akiya Ogawa, Takumi Mizuno}}</ref>以及4-溴苯硼酸的碘化反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=RSC Advances|volume=5|issue=103|language=en|issn=2046-2069|date=2015|pages=84910–84919|doi=10.1039/C5RA18820B|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C5RA18820B|title=A practical and general ipso iodination of arylboronic acids using N-iodomorpholinium iodide (NIMI) as a novel iodinating agent: mild and regioselective synthesis of aryliodides|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=R. H. Tale, G. K. Toradmal, V. B. Gopula}}</ref>。

==性质==
它和[[硫|硫]]、[[氢氧化锂|氢氧化锂]]在DMF中反应（[[碘化亚铜|CuI]]催化），可以得到4,4'-二溴苯硫醚。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Organometallics|volume=32|issue=19|language=en|issn=0276-7333|date=2013-10-14|pages=5514–5522|doi=10.1021/om400784w|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/om400784w|title=Use of Base Control To Provide High Selectivity between Diaryl Thioether and Diaryl Disulfide for C–S Coupling Reactions of Aryl Halides and Sulfur and a Mechanistic Study|accessdate=2020-10-21|author=Hsing-Ying Chen, Wei-Te Peng, Ying-Hsien Lee, Yu-Lun Chang, Yen-Jen Chen, Yi-Chun Lai, Nai-Yuan Jheng, Hsuan-Ying Chen}}</ref>它和[[乙烯基溴化镁|乙烯基溴化镁]]反应，可以得到4-溴苯乙烯。<ref>Bumagin, N. A.; Andryukhova, N. P.; Beletskaya, I. P. Catalyst for cross-​coupling of vinylmagnesium bromide with aryl iodides{{ru}}. ''Izvestiya Akademii Nauk SSSR, Seriya Khimicheskaya'', 1987. 7: 1681-1682. ISSN: 0002-3353.</ref>
